step.screen:
Cron     : &systemd; timer
-------- : ----------------------------
@reboot  : OnBootSec=1s
@yearly  : OnCalendar=*-01-01 00:00:00
@annually: OnCalendar=*-01-01 00:00:00
@monthly : OnCalendar=*-*-01 00:00:00
@weekly  : OnCalendar=Sun *-*-* 00:00:00
@daily   : OnCalendar=*-*-* 00:00:00
@hourly  : OnCalendar=*-*-* *:00:00
